parameters:
\SE[65]The atmosphere is so gloomy.... \!\SE[60]The scenery
looks similar, so I might get lost....

\SE[9]I think we're moving forward... but... \SE[8]It's hard
to tell just from this situation...
\SE[4]Huh? Why are there people in a place like this?
\SE[2]You... do you know me...? \SE[3]Have we met before...?

\SE[4]Ah, I remember! \SE[15]You're the person who gave us
our mother...!

\SE[17]... I didn't give her to you. \SE[12] Return Luna
right now. Otherwise...
\SE[4]Ah, that's right. \SE[3]Hmm... What should I do...

\SE[0]Yeah, I'm fine now. \. I've had a lot of fun....
\!\SE[0]And I've made some friends here too.

\SE[33]However, I wonder if that child will dislike it....
\!\SE[3]Look...\. The black one. \!\SE[3]That child is
very attached to Mommy. \.They will probably throw a
tantrum....

\SE[4]Well, if you want her back, why don't you come and
meet me like this? \!\SE[0]You could just forcefully take
her from that child. \.I don't really mind either way.

\SE[4]But how did you get in? \SE[3]Only we should be
able to come to this place.... \SE[4]Ah, I see. Is that how?

\SE[3]I see. So the girl behind us is together with us.
\SE[0]In that case, we can do the same thing, right?

\SE[2]But why did you come here? \!\SE[3]If you make a
mistake, you'll fall endlessly. It's dangerous, you know?
\SE[2]Ah, um... \SE[3]I came to cure Melia-chan's illness.

\SE[4]Huh?! You guys too...!? \SE[0]If that's the case, then
we're not alone. Let's all work together!

\SE[2]...Sometimes, you know. I would come and play in
Melia's dream world. \SE[0] She was my first friend in this
world over here....

\SE[2]I knew that I was being bothered by a troublesome
person, but whenever that person sees me coming, they
immediately hide... \SE[3]So far, I haven't been able to
kill them...

\SE[16]But today seems different. \!\SE[0]Maybe I'm being
drawn to the scent of a human. \.With this, I can definitely
kill them.

\SE[37]But if only I go, they might escape again....
\SE[15]So, let's cooperate, okay? \SE[15]...That way, our
chances of winning will be higher, right?
\SE[17]Do you think I can trust 'you all'? \SE[12]

\SE[3]Hmm... But it might be difficult for 'you all' to deal
with 'that person', the 'human', you know? \SE[4]'Laura'
might survive though...
\SE[33]The big sister behind you will definitely die.

\SE[2]And also, Melia... \SE[3]If we continue like this,
you'll end up dying, right?

\SE[9]I also want to help Melia! I don't want to lose my
first friend. \SE[8]Please. Take me with you?

\SE[12]Laura-san, even if we talk here... Melia-chan and
Lunaroa- san won't be saved. \SE[14]...As for me, I want to
increase the chances of their survival even just a little. I
believe her help will be a great strength.

\SE[24]... Fine, I get it. \SE[64] We should go together,
right...

\SE[16]Ahaha...! What a wonderful answer! \SE[0]Even if it's
just for a little while, please take care of me!
